sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User
  participant I as identity-nostr package
  participant K as Kernel
  participant R as Nostr Relay
  participant M as Plugin Marketplace

  U->>I: createIdentity()
  I->>I: generate keypair
  I-->>U: npub + secret management metadata

  U->>I: publishProfile(event)
  I->>I: sign event (NIP-01)
  I->>R: publish signed event
  R-->>I: ack event id

  U->>K: discover plugins
  K->>M: fetch NIP-89 metadata refs
  M-->>K: plugin descriptors + artifact links
  K->>R: verify publisher key and latest event
  R-->>K: signed metadata events
  K-->>U: trusted plugin candidates
